---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="About — Camille Aubert"
  description="Learn more about Camille Aubert, Senior Full-stack Developer and Solutions Architect focused on AI systems, scalable architecture, and industrial-grade delivery."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Engineering reliable intelligence for production environments.</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      I am a Senior Full-stack Developer and Solutions Architect committed to the “1% excellence”
      philosophy. I specialize in deploying AI as a core performance multiplier within industrial
      environments, bridging the gap between cutting-edge research and reliable production systems.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Approach</h2>
    <p>
      Architecture is the new productivity. I build deterministic, scalable systems that shift focus
      from manual code execution to the orchestration of autonomous intelligent agents.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>What I do</h2>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>AI Systems Architecture (RAG, LLM, Multi-agent orchestration).</li>
      <li>High-Performance Full-Stack Development (PHP/Laravel, React).</li>
      <li>Industrial Infrastructure Automation (Docker, AWS, CI/CD).</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
